data.description: Charming and tastefully renovated 2 bedroom/1.5 bath bungalow in historic Dignowity. Huge covered front porch and deck. New flooring, drywall, plumbing, roof and kitchen appliances within the last 2 years, along with state-of-the-art electric ductless mini-split AC/heating system.  Fenced yard, mature pecan and orange trees, large concrete parking apron immediately adjacent to side entry. Please see add'l seller disclosure for revisions made to home and explanation of intentional slope at side interior door. Near downtown, easy access to highways, restaurants, shopping and the Pearl! Verify room measurements and schools if important. Move in ready!
